description: "Auto-export game data to a user-chosen zip and auto-import newer zip on startup (newest wins). Mostly useful on Android phones to export save data automatically outside of protected android folders. In conjunction with FolderSync or similar cloud sync apps, you could create sutomatic synchronization of PC and mobile saves."